source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000010_GAIA<tab>I'm drawing out the Darkness. Get ready!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000020_RYNE<tab>It worked, Gaia! We've done it!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000030_RYNE<tab>So this all took place a hundred years ago...
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000040_RYNE<tab>But what does it have to do with Gaia?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000040_RYNE<tab>Mais quel rapport... avec les souvenirs de Gaïa...<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000050_RYNE<tab>I know this place...! It's the gaol in Eulmore!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000050_RYNE<tab>Je reconnais cet endroit... C'est la prison d'Eulmore<var 1D /var>!?
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000060_RYNE<tab>Peu importe ce qui se dresse sur notre route...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000070_RYNE<tab>...we will never give up hope!

target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000080_EDEN3BOSS3<tab>Je ne souhaiterai jamais rien d'autre que ton bonheur...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000100_EDEN3BOSS4<tab>One that we may share for all eternity.

target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000110_RYNE<tab>Sa conscience... Elle est toujours là, quelque part...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000120_RYNE<tab>I won't give up on our future, Gaia! No matter what!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000120_RYNE<tab>Gaïa... tiens bon<var 1D /var>! Je ne renoncerai pas à notre avenir<var 1D /var>!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000140_EDEN3BOSS5<tab>Dans un autre corps... Dans une autre vie...
